_sText:
Made by request for a friends map. Reduced from 6 to 4 digits. 

Password is 1-5-3-7. can be changed and edited very simply, just look at the keypad.

Can have up to 9 numbers (but then it doesn't work). Very simple, very basic, does not provide duplicate numbers and does not make you restart if you press the right number twice.

Made in about 10 secs XD

You don't have to give me credit for it, but it would be most welcome if you did so.
